choices.text:
1. Add null checks for the record passed to the mapTerminalRecordToTerminalModel() method to avoid potential NullPointerException.
2. Use @NonNull annotation for parameters of the getTerminalById() method to ensure that null values are not passed to this method. 
3. Improve code readability by adding more comments to describe the code written.
4. If applicable, add specific exception types in the IllegalArgumentException thrown when terminalId is null.
